    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to a great variety of furniture including barbers' chairs, wheelchairs, and space-saving office furniture; designed to solve a particular problem.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
